From 72f213a7b3f29fca1ca202067f6068c3dbe22b99 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Rainbaby <rainbaby@outlook.jp>
Date: Sat, 4 Jul 2026 20:21:43 +0900
Subject: [PATCH 02/14] File_MmtTlv: probe HEVC/AAC elementary streams for
 codec detail

Feed each asset's reassembled MFU data units to a child File_Hevc/File_Aac
(Annex-B for HEVC, LOAS for LATM AAC) and Merge onto the stream: video gets
resolution/profile/bit depth/HDR, audio channels/rate. Bounded by a single
64 MB probe budget, sized for sparse 8K RAPs.

Signed-off-by: Rainbaby <rainbaby@outlook.jp>
---
 Source/MediaInfo/Multiple/File_MmtTlv.cpp | 255 +++++++++++++++++++++-
 Source/MediaInfo/Multiple/File_MmtTlv.h   |  27 +++
 2 files changed, 276 insertions(+), 6 deletions(-)

